in jenkins integratoin with docker build and push
=====================================================
download a plugin called cloudbees docker build and publish
create a job and go to build->select docker build and publish->enter repository name(docker image tag)->and enter docker hub login details like username and password, give ID to use this ID for future use somewhere to recognize.


